<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.6">
<l>takkaṉ vēḷvi takartta talaivaṉ</l>
<l>tukkan tuṭaitta tuṇaiva rūrpōl</l>
<l>ekka liṭunuṇ maṇalmē leṅkum</l>
<l>kokkiṉ paḻamvīḻ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where mango fruits fall everywhere</l>
<l>On fine sand which is cast up [in] heaps,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the protector who removed</l>
<l>The distress of the god who smashed Dakṣa’s sacrifice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
